        function Cal(obj, cellindex, num, roletype) {&#13;
            var headerpreid = obj.id.split("_cb")[0];&#13;
&#13;
            switch (num) {&#13;
                case 1:&#13;
                    document.getElementById(headerpreid + "_cbOvecod2All").checked = false;&#13;
                    document.getElementById(headerpreid + "_cbOvecod3All").checked = false;&#13;
                    break;&#13;
                case 2:&#13;
                    document.getElementById(headerpreid + "_cbOvecod1All").checked = false;&#13;
                    document.getElementById(headerpreid + "_cbOvecod3All").checked = false;&#13;
                    break;&#13;
                case 3:&#13;
                    document.getElementById(headerpreid + "_cbOvecod1All").checked = false;&#13;
                    document.getElementById(headerpreid + "_cbOvecod2All").checked = false;&#13;
                    break;&#13;
            }&#13;
&#13;
            var table = document.getElementById("gvAttn");&#13;
            var len = table.rows.length;&#13;
 &#13;
            var txt;&#13;
            var wrkdat;&#13;
            var sftcod;&#13;
            var holcod;&#13;
            var entday;&#13;
            var stwday;&#13;
            var entdat;&#13;
            var stwkhr;&#13;
            var multim;&#13;
            var strehr;&#13;
            var enrehr;&#13;
            var preid;&#13;
            var emplid;&#13;
            var appnum;&#13;
            var neweid;&#13;
            var sfttyp;&#13;
            var mealyn;&#13;
            &#13;
            for (var i=1 ; i &lt; len; i++) {&#13;
                try {&#13;
                   var preid = (table.rows[i].cells[cellindex].innerHTML.split("_gvcbOvecod" + num)[0]).replace('"', ''); /*此处添加替换*/&#13;
                    wrkdat = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvlblWrkdat").split("id=")[1]).innerHTML;&#13;
                    sftcod = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvlblSftcod").split("id=")[1]).innerHTML;&#13;
                    holcod = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvhdHolcod").split("id=")[1]).value;&#13;
                    entday = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvhdStartDateTime").split("id=")[1]).value;&#13;
                    stwday = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvhdEndDateTime").split("id=")[1]).value;&#13;
                    entdat = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvlblEntdat").split("id=")[1]).innerHTML;&#13;
                    stwkhr = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvlblStwkhr").split("id=")[1]).innerHTML;&#13;
                    multim = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvlblMultim").split("id=")[1]).innerHTML;&#13;
                    strehr = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvhdStrehr").split("id=")[1]).value;&#13;
                    enrehr = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvhdEnrehr").split("id=")[1]).value;&#13;
                    emplid = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvlblEmplid").split("id=")[1]).innerHTML;&#13;
                    neweid = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvhdNeweid").split("id=")[1]).value;&#13;
                    sfttyp = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvhdSfttyp").split("id=")[1]).value;&#13;
                    appnum = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvhdAppnum").split("id=")[1]).value;&#13;
                    mealyn = document.getElementById((preid + "_gvlblMealyn").split("id=")[1]).innerHTML;&#13;
                    txt = preid + "_gvcbOvecod" + num;&#13;
                    var rowCheckBox = document.getElementById(txt.split("id=")[1]);&#13;
                    rowCheckBox.checked = obj.checked;&#13;
                    Cal_hrs(rowCheckBox, wrkdat, sftcod, holcod, entday, stwday, entdat, stwkhr, roletype, multim, strehr, enrehr, appnum, emplid, neweid, sfttyp, mealyn);&#13;
                }&#13;
                catch (e) {&#13;
                }&#13;
            }&#13;
        }&#13;

        function GetReport(typcod) {&#13;
            var strdat = document.getElementById("txtFromDate").value;&#13;
            var enddat = document.getElementById("txtToDate").value;&#13;
            var depcod = document.getElementById("txtDepcod").value;&#13;
            if (depcod == "") {&#13;
                depcod = document.getElementById("ddlDepcod").value;&#13;
            }&#13;
            if (depcod == "") {&#13;
                depcod = "1";&#13;
            }&#13;
            var login = document.getElementById("lblLoginID").innerHTML;&#13;
            if ((strdat != "" &amp;&amp; enddat != "") || typcod == "3") {&#13;
                if (typcod == "1") {&#13;
                    window.open("http://172.16.2.88/ReportServer/Pages/ReportViewer.aspx?%2fQCMCHR%2f%e8%80%83%e5%8b%a4%e6%8a%a5%e8%a1%a8%2fOverhr_Report&amp;depcod=" + depcod + "&amp;strdat=" + strdat + "&amp;enddat=" + enddat + "&amp;login=" + login + "&amp;rs%3aCommand=Render&amp;rs%3AFormat=EXCEL");&#13;
                }&#13;
                if (typcod == "2") {&#13;
                    window.open("http://172.16.2.88/ReportServer/Pages/ReportViewer.aspx?%2fQCMCHR%2f%e8%80%83%e5%8b%a4%e6%8a%a5%e8%a1%a8%2f%e9%83%a8%e9%97%a8%e5%8a%a0%e7%8f%ad%e6%b1%87%e6%80%bb&amp;emplid=" + login + "&amp;strdat=" + strdat + "&amp;enddat=" + enddat + "&amp;rs%3aCommand=Render&amp;rs%3AFormat=EXCEL");&#13;
                }&#13;
                if (typcod == "3") {&#13;
                    window.open("http://172.16.2.88/ReportServer/Pages/ReportViewer.aspx?%2fQCMCHR%2f%u8003%u52e4%u62a5%u8868%2f%u8fde%u7eed%u5de5%u4f5cN%u5929%u62a5%u8868&amp;Login=" + login + "&amp;rs%3aCommand=Render");&#13;
                }&#13;
            }&#13;
            else {&#13;
                alert("请输入统计日期");&#13;
            }&#13;
        }&#13;
